For Creating service :  ng g service services/services
For Creating Components inside folder : ng g c students/add
Bootstrap : npm install bootstrap --save
            -- goto angular.josn file  :   In styles parameter

            "styles": [
              "src/styles.css",
              "node_modules/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css",
              "/node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"

            ],



To create Forms need to import in app.module.ts file : import { FormsModule } from '@angular/forms';



To create class in model : ng g class Model/ApiResponse